  "hiringCompany": {
    "uen": "202117339E",
    "description": "<p>Amidst the breathtaking landscapes of Yunnan, a flavor born from nature thrives—fresh yet primal, rich yet pure. This is the unique charm of Yunnan ecological hotpot. Carrying this authentic gift from nature, we have traveled across mountains and seas to bring its taste and culture to Singapore, allowing more people to experience the purity and warmth of Yunnan.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>A Taste Closely Connected to Nature<br>\n— What defines the natural essence of our broth? It is the beauty of mountains, rivers, and the boundless sea.<br>\nYunnan, known as China’s “Natural Oxygen Bar,” boasts a rich ecological environment that gives rise to the distinct flavors of its hotpot. Unlike traditional hotpots with heavy broths, Yunnan ecological hotpot follows the philosophy of \"natural, green, and healthy.\" Using fresh local ingredients from Singapore, we respect nature’s bounty, ensuring that from the broth to the dishes, every bite retains the ingredient’s authentic essence.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Where Culture Meets Cuisine<br>\nYunnan ecological hotpot is more than just a meal—it is a cultural experience.<br>\nFrom the majestic mountains of Yunnan to the vibrant streets of Singapore, we use hotpot as a medium to share the rich heritage,<br>\ncustoms, and traditions of Yunnan in a contemporary and refined manner.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>MISSION<br>\nTransform flavors into a tangible delight,<br>\nallowing the joy of dining to be<br>\neffortlessly expressed.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>VISION<br>\nUnite the world at one table.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>VALUES<br>\nSincerity<br>\nHonesty, consistency, and respect in all aspects of life.<br>\nEthics<br>\nAdhering to social morals, ensuring harmony and integrity.<br>\nOrder<br>\nMaintaining a structured approach for steady progress.</p>",
    "name": "BROTH BEYOND SINGAPORE PTE. LTD.",
